console.log(date,'to date'); }; const handleFromTime=(event)=>{ setFromTime((event.target.value)) console.log(event.target.value,'from time'); } const handleToTime=(event)=>{ settoTime((event.target.value)) console.log(event.target.value,'to time'); setlist(response.data.Models) }).catch((error)=>{ console.log(error); }) await axios({ url:`${REACT_APP_SERVER_URL}/api/web/maker/list`, method:"GET" }).then((response)=>{ console.log(response.data,'brand'); setlist(response.data) }).catch((error)=>{ console.log(error); }) } const sortedProducts = [...list].sort((a, b) => { if (sortByLowToHigh) { return a.Offer_Rate - b.Offer_Rate; } else if (sortByHighToLow) { return b.Offer_Rate - a.Offer_Rate;
